label: All the Flights in the World
description: Two hours of flight data collected by OpenSky Network on September 3rd 2019
detail: This dataset contains two hours of flight data collected using the live API of [OpenSky Network](https://opensky-network.org). The color of the flights is based on country of origin. 18 thousands flights are recorded during the two hour period. The path drops over the seas due to lack of satellite coverage.

label: California Earthquakes
description: Location, magnitude and type of 2.5+ magnitude earthquakes in california.
detail: This dataset contains a list of 2.5+ magnitude earthquakes in california. It is gathered from the [USGS website](https://earthquake.usgs.gov/data/data.php) and contains multiple properties (location, magnitude, and type) for each single entry.

label: NYC Taxi Trips
description: A small sample of yellow and green taxi trip records in New York City.
detail: The yellow and green taxi trip records include fields capturing pick-up and drop-off dates/times, pick-up and drop-off locations, trip distances, itemized fares, rate types, payment types, and driver-reported passenger counts. Data is downloaded from [NYC Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC)](https://www1.nyc.gov/site/tlc/about/tlc-trip-record-data.page)

label: San Francisco Elevation Contour
description: Elevation contours of San Francisco mainland and Treasure Island/Yerba Island.

label: New York City Population by Census Tract
description: This dataset contains the 2010 Census tract population data of NYC.

label: San Francisco Street Tree Map
description: A 3d hexbin density map showing every single streets in San Francisco

label: Commute Pattern in England and Wales
description: A origin destination map using 3d arcs to show commute patterns of England and Wales residence

label: $2+ Million Homes Built in Los Angeles Since 2006
description: Map showing new homes valued over $2,000,000 built in Los Angeles county since 2006

description: Pittsburgh travel times before and during heavy inclement weather conditions
